!! Colors and Breath Weapons

Dragons are magical creatures whose innate power fuels their dreaded breath weapons and other preternatural abilities. These breath weapons are fearsome, but take up to a minute to recharge after use. 

The [[type|damage type]] of a dragon's breath weapon can be determined by the color of the dragon's scales; see the below tables. The dragon is also resistant or immune to that type of damage. Note that metallic dragons have two different kinds of magic breath they can use; one destructive, and one more subtle or utilitarian. Chromatic dragons only have a destructive breath weapon, but it is typically more powerful than that of comparable metallic dragons.

